Mr. GOLDSWORTHY: Some people have suggested that, for reliability, these aids should be duplicated. What has been done about duplicating the ground equipment? And has anyone followed up Mr. Fraser's mention of an ultra narrow-beam ILS, for instance by using it as one of the pair, in a duplicated installation?
